OL,3,CCarer jailed after forcing young
OL,4,Cwheelchair user to crawl on floor
OL,6,FA carer has been jailed for 12 months
OL,7,Ffollowing her "appalling" abuse of a
OL,8,Fvulnerable disabled teenager.
OL,10,FJoana Da Mata Viana Martins, 42,
OL,11,Fmocked the 18-year-old woman, shouted
OL,12,Fin her face and deliberately took away
OL,13,Fher wheelchair so she had to crawl
OL,14,Faround her flat.
OL,16,FMartins was also physically
OL,17,Fintimidating and in one case, forced
OL,18,Fthe woman to eat until she was sick.
