OL,3,CCarer jailed after forcing young
OL,4,Cwheelchair user to crawl on floor
OL,6,FInvestigating Officer, Detective
OL,7,FSergeant Martin Davies, says: "This is
OL,8,Fan appalling crime, whereby Joana
OL,9,FMartins abused the victim who was a
OL,10,Fvulnerable young female who relied on
OL,11,Fher for care."
OL,13,FMartins was a team leader at a care
OL,14,Fagency and was expected to guide less
OL,15,Fexperienced staff.
OL,17,FHowever, it was a junior carer who
OL,18,Fraised the alarm about her behaviour
OL,19,Fon 27 September 2022.
