OL,6,FIn a landmark case at Jersey's Royal
OL,7,FCourt, Martins was found guilty of two
OL,8,Fcounts of ill-treatment and wilful
OL,9,Fneglect under the Capacity and Self-
OL,10,FDetermination Law.
OL,12,FThe legislation was brought in to
OL,13,Fbetter protect the most vulnerable
OL,14,Fpeople in society and Martins is the
OL,15,Ffirst to be sentenced under it.
OL,17,FIn sentencing, Commissioner Alan
OL,18,FBinnington concluded Martins did not
OL,19,Fprovide her client with dignity,
OL,20,Fhumanity and respect.
